---
description: No AI/Cursor attribution in git or PRs
alwaysApply: true
---

Never add "Made-with: Cursor", "Co-authored-by: Cursor", "cursoragent", or any AI/Cursor attribution to commits, PRs, or code comments.

When committing, use only: `git commit -m "message"` with no `--trailer` flags.

If a commit message would include Cursor attribution, strip it before committing.
